fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.plugins.devs

Interface CoordinatorPluginI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.CoordinatorI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.interfaces.EventsExchangingI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.interfaces.ModelDescriptionI, ModelStateAccessI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.interfaces.ParentNotificationI, fr.sorbonne_u.components.PluginI, java.io.Serializable, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.SimulationManagementI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.SimulatorI, SimulatorPluginI, SimulatorPluginManagementI
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RTCoordinatorPluginI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoordinatorPlugin, RTCoordinatorPlugin

    public interface CoordinatorPluginI
extends SimulatorPluginI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.CoordinatorI
    The interface CoordinatorPluginI declares the methods that a coordinator plug-in must implement.

    Description

    This interface extends the DEBS simulation corresponding interface with methods used to perform the connections of a component holding a coupled model to the components holding its submodels.

    Invariant

     invariant      true

    Created on : 2018-06-14

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
